<?php $__env->startSection('content'); ?><p>Newcastle welcome Brighton to St James' Park this afternoon as Steve Bruce's men look to build on Premier League opening win.  </p>

<p>The Magpies were comfortable winners over West Ham last week with summer signing Callum Wilson scoring on his debut.</p>

<p>But the face a difficult task to make it two wins out of two against a promising Brighton side who gave Frank Lampard's Chelsea a tough game on the opening weekend of the season. </p>

<p>Sportsmail's SAM BLITZ will provide live coverage of Newcastle vs Brighton including score, lineups and build-up.</p>
